Did you like them?
 

00:07:02.980 --> 00:07:16.850
Student:  Yeah.
 

00:07:16.850 --> 00:07:20.269
Prof: Great.
 

00:07:20.269 --> 00:07:22.350
We're going to see part of each
slide--there we go.

00:07:22.350 --> 00:07:28.139
We've got two cases this week,
