00:07:43.470 --> 00:07:50.817
The idea of abrupt change,
of equilibrium always being

00:07:50.817 --> 00:07:55.829
dislodged,
equilibrium always disrupted,

00:07:55.829 --> 00:08:02.470
and the cardiothoracic systems
