instant photography,

00:44:28.219 --> 00:44:30.369
what the founder founded,
so they were--

00:44:30.369 --> 00:44:33.181
because that kind of cult,
and if they weren't really

00:44:33.181 --> 00:44:36.050
moving on towards other things
and improving on it.

00:44:36.050 --> 00:44:37.978
Prof: Okay,
so a merger might well have

00:44:37.978 --> 00:44:38.880
been the best play.
 

00:44:38.880 --> 00:44:42.480
Now why would it--what would
make it hard to do?

00:44:42.480 --> 00:44:45.942
Student:  I think it's
the culture of the company that

00:44:45.942 --> 00:44:48.003
